Beth Heinly is a performance artist and curator who draws comics under the pseudonym 3:00. At Little Berlin she was one of the original members after the group collectivized in 2009. During her membership she cultivated the Zine Library and curated various performance based events.Past work at Little Berlin:March 2009: ProspectsOctober 2009: Breaking NewsMay 2011: VASST.infoSeptember 2012: PRRRSONA
